Come on, will.
Give us one of your recitations.

887
00:54:20,724 --> 00:54:22,676
Oh, no.
Come on, will.

888
00:54:22,708 --> 00:54:23,772
I've forgotten all that.

889
00:54:23,908 --> 00:54:25,172
That nice one--
Robert Browning.

890
00:54:25,205 --> 00:54:27,189
A bit of Browning.Come on.
All right, then.

